Boundary Value Analysis (BVA) 
Focused on checking the minimum and maximum values at the boundaries of the range, as the errors most likely occurs in this area.
e.g. User is asked to enter age. Range 18-56
BVA values: 
* 3 point: 17, 18, 19 and 55, 56, 57
* 2 point: 17, 18 and 56, 57

